ridos|title=[FOTOS Y VIDEO] Colapso de puente Cancura deja un muerto y seis heridos|last=Tele 13|date=|website=t13.cl|access-date=20 February 2019}}</ref>\n|One section directly over the river Rahue collapsed\n|The bridge was under surveillance and undergoing maintenance work as several problems had been reported over the prior year. The Directorate of Hydraulic Works had reported only days prior to the accident to the Ministry of Public Works that mitigation measures were necessary as riverflow changes were causing potential undermining of the bridge foundations. Other suspected causes were improperly regulated extraction of sand and stones from the riverbed<ref>{{cite web|url=http://t13.cl/noticia/nacional/oficio-advertia-al-mop-problemas-puente-cancura|title=Oficio advert\u00eda al MOP sobre problemas en el puente Cancura|last=Tele 13|date=|website=t13.cl|access-date=20 February 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|Zhejiang bridge collapse\n|[[Hangzhou City]] \u2013 [[Zhejiang]]\n|[[China|People's Republic of China]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2018|July|28}}\n|\n|\n|8 dead<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2018-07/28/c_137352764.htm|title=8 dead, 3 injured in lounge bridge collapse - Xinhua - English.news.cn|author=|date=|website=www.Xinhuanet.com|access-date=20 February 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[Ponte Morandi]] motorway bridge collapse\n|[[Genoa]] \u2013 [[Liguria]]\n|[[Italy]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2018|August|14}}\n| Viaduct incorporating a [[cable-stayed bridge]]\n|\n| 43 dead<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2018/08/18/news/crollo_genova_trovati_i_corpi_di_tre_dei_dispersi-204360358/|title=Crollo Genova, trovato l'ultimo disperso sotto le macerie: \u00e8 l'operaio Mirko. Muore uno dei feriti, le vittime totali sono 43|author=|date=18 August 2018|website=Repubblica.it|access-date=20 February 2019}}</ref>\n|{{Convert|210|m|adj=on}} section of the bridge collapsed\n|[[File:Ponte morandi crollato.jpg|thumb|upright=.80|Ponte Morandi after the collapse;